::Prowl::

Prowl heard every thought of IR's loud and clear, guilt and other
depressing feelings beginning to build up in him. He didn't mean to go
against her wishes like that, he just wanted the Maximals to live.
Prowl nods and steps back.

"Allright," he says. It wouldn't be good to stay here right now
anyways. He would try to talk to her when she calms down. Prowl
reluctantly turns around, but doesn't fly off yet, hesistating and
looking back at Iron Raptor.
